item.title: Jihyun Kim
item.description: Hi! I’m a self-motivated senior undergraduate student double major in English Language and Literature and Computer Science. I’m currently a research assisant in Hardware Security laboratory at Hongik University. I’m broadly interested in big data and AI related research topics, where deep learning models are theoretically capable of, especially sequence models. education & experience Bachelor of English, Computer Science - Hongik University (expected October 2020) Minor: Business Administraion
